    "license": "MIT",
    "name": "De novo",
    "report": {
        "markdown": "\n# De novo assembly report\n\n## Workflow Inputs\n```galaxy\ninvocation_inputs()\n```\n\n## Quality control\n### FastQC forward reads\n\n```galaxy\nhistory_dataset_display(output=\"forward_qc\")\n```\n\n### FastQC reverse reads\n\n```galaxy\nhistory_dataset_display(output=\"reverse_qc\")\n```\n\n### FastQC after pairing and filtering\n\n```galaxy\nhistory_dataset_display(output=\"paired_qc\")\n```\n\n## Contig1\n### Consensus sequence (obtained from reads containing the primer)\n\n```galaxy\nhistory_dataset_display(output=\"contig1\")\n```\n\n### BLASTN\n\n```galaxy\nhistory_dataset_display(output=\"blastn1\")\n```\n\n### Final consensus\n#### Elongation of the consensus\n\n```galaxy\nhistory_dataset_display(output=\"consensus_contig1\")\n```\n\n### Browser\nVisualisation of reads mapped to the consensus\n\n```galaxy\nhistory_dataset_display(output=\"browser1\")\n```\n\n### Metadata file\n\n```galaxy\nhistory_dataset_display(output=\"metadata1\")\n```\n\n\n## Contig2\n#### if the primer has been used more than once\n\n### Consensus sequence (obtained from reads containing the primer)\n\n```galaxy\nhistory_dataset_display(output=\"contig2\")\n```\n\n### BLASTN\n\n```galaxy\nhistory_dataset_display(output=\"blastn2\")\n```\n\n### Final consensus\n#### Elongation of the consensus\n\n```galaxy\nhistory_dataset_display(output=\"consensus_contig2\")\n```\n\n### Browser\nVisualisation of the reads mapping onto the consensus\n\n```galaxy\nhistory_dataset_display(output=\"browser2\")\n```\n\n### Metadata file\n\n```galaxy\nhistory_dataset_display(output=metadata2)\n```\n"
    },
